g src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:06:47.000Z","msg":"★支那好治癒gif貼圖區！（10）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2393089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2393089</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJGYkpY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJGYkpY.png&h=88f71e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqrT3vv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqrT3vv.gif&h=20885470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快d入去帶風向，攪唔掂"},{"pid":"7810522dac5ac93c4d24618e84f11ed6611fbdbb","tid":2424260,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"成班藍屍圍爐駛撚理"},{"pid":"1a598b7d397acba213e03fb324616e265905cf28","tid":2424260,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"美金同港元脫勾先係"},{"pid":"477123a417725bcb4d5d58a5d973dede0bab75e9","tid":2424260,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bb7f7805d5325dadc3b473342ad97071e3d1a119","tid":2424260,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"[戇鳩警報器: 黃世澤 | martin oei | 交加街38號 ] 警世 黃世澤係令大家用唔到BNO移民既始作俑者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423877</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:13:43.000Z","msg":"又係你件垃圾，我一早預言會有你呢 D PR 出黎抹黑 BNO 手足：<br />\n有關 BNO 出現極端分化現象 - 個別 POST / USER 細心分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2408756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2408756</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><ins><em><span class=\"x-large\">第三類：攻擊特定人士減低 BNO 資訊傳播性</span></em></ins><br />\n<br />\n例如 Martin Oei 手足好多人都知佢係 BNO 5+1 政策其中一個 contributor，對整套移民政策法律都非常熟悉，經常於其 Youtube 頻道傳播有關 BNO 既正確資訊，但由於走資問題會損害中共利益，所以飽受五毛黨攻擊：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>黃世澤 入境條例修訂想阻 BNO走 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2404932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2404932</a><br />\n黃世澤 中國驚BNO同加拿大、澳洲救生艇計劃賤招盡出 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2401236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2401236</a><br />\n黃世澤 林鄭月娥意圖變相阻BNO離港 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2396831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2396831</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而最近吳志森指出港共對 BNO 手足惡行及提醒香港人，亦遭五毛攻擊及強行拉 POST：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>吳志森 林鄭最開心嘅日子係一家人喺英國， 成家人嘅英國籍點攞番嚟？ 點解要做「二等公民」？ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2391747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2391747</a><br />\n吳志森 禁BNO擔任公職，包括做公務員？ 剝奪投票權，幾百萬香港人受影響，走得更堅決！<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2367448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2367448</a><br />\n吳志森 申請BNO人數破晒紀錄， 超過百萬港人會逃到英國？<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2350164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2350164</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩者均遭人身攻擊及抹黑 *留意：擇文者本人為共諜-白兵打手：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>黃之鋒公報私仇,斷章取義,無知,無持續進修,恐懼無領導地位,過橋抽板,濫權,眷戀光環,彈起只係時勢,有做獨裁者潛質 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229581</a><br />\n吳志森：根據一分事實，講一分真話，反制BNO後會唔會跟住搞埋擁有雙重國籍嘅香港人？<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390171</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟作為一位提倡用 BNO 離開攻擊中共既小小手足，貼文亦多次遭五毛攻擊。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"03ecdbe3743cdb6c6b9e93b903025f8d7bb69903","tid":2424260,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8gXi41nmeBc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8gXi41nmeBc&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=a5adde99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8gXi41nmeBc</a>"},{"pid":"ddf7add1de6844c1d19f2b3a3343a17ed1b985bb","tid":2424260,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c9302e0825948b941c76c054e3dea572fc5f61e","tid":2424260,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc03de691fa53ca1d6704616c09df3bfcb402b14",